A discrete, motivational study timer keychain.

Functions:

- When pressed, the keychain gives motivational messages to encourage you to stay focused
- When held, the keychain will start a timer for your study session or break 
- After a hour of study, the keychain will give you a reminder to take a break and drink some water
- When held again, the keychain will end the current session and reset.

The keychain is designed to be small,rechargable and portable. Acting as a study companion of sorts. It has a keycap which can be pressed as well as
a small screen to display a timer and messages. Has a speaker to announce messages and volume nob to adjust the sound level.

